CustomField.description: Initially created as part of DCP-1298 for the Date on which the Proposal is sent. This is an automated field. As part of DCP-51592 field label was changed to 'Quote Generated On' as this field indicates the date quote was generated. NOTE: API Name was still retained as 'Proposal_Sent_On__c'
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Date on which Quote is generated.
CustomField.label: Quote Generated on
